2DA V1.0
*
FILE        STAT        CHECKCOL    READCOL
fatigmod    FATIGUE     -1          0

# master file determing which tables and stats affect luck
# the columns dictate which tables to consult at which offsets
# STAT is the stat the value of which will be used for the lookup
# CHECKCOL is for what column to check against, -1 being the row name
# READCOL is for which column to read from
